Name: Trap Labs
About the game: Help Billy get to the top of Trap Labs! Each floor of the questionable corporate building features a unique action puzzle that challenges your skills and wit. Play online with friends up to 16 players per game! Get Billy across the room by dodging trap puzzles that fires in repeating patterns (inspired by bounds and mazes from StarCraft and WarCraft) 100 levels of story campaign that will keep you busy for hours! Another 100 levels of fast paced Level Up mode for that sweet challenge! Compete against players around the globe for top spot on leaderboards! Play online-multiplayer in co-op and race style maps Customize Billy in variety of colors and over 30 weird and funny looking hats True cross-platform/cross-device online multiplayer play (Windows, Mac, Android, iOS)
